Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.590 --> 00:00:09.059
Clubs serve an important part of our school's mission to create well-rounded citizens

00:00:09.060 --> 00:00:13.800
Extracurricular clubs are held after school and all students must join

00:00:13.880 --> 00:00:16.520
an extracurricular Club or team each term

00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:19.540
There's a wide variety of offerings run by Bodwell teachers

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:23.760
Clubs usually meet once occasionally twice each week during the term

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:27.740
Students joining a sports team have more commitment during a competitive season

00:00:27.740 --> 00:00:31.640
involving frequent practices and playing matches with other schools

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:35.160
Clubs and sports teams are an opportunity for students

00:00:35.180 --> 00:00:39.120
together with teachers to get to know one another through common interests.

00:00:39.260 --> 00:00:42.080
They are often away at students can develop a hobby,

00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:45.700
improve their interpersonal skills, and widen their life experience.

00:00:45.700 --> 00:00:49.920
We have several music clubs such as the concert band and rock band.

00:00:53.260 --> 00:00:56.729
We have art clubs for students that need to build an art portfolio.

00:00:57.520 --> 00:01:01.709
Some clubs are more connected to academic areas like the Model United Nations,

00:01:02.680 --> 00:01:05.159
public speaking, chess, or the robotics team.

00:01:09.079 --> 00:01:13.989
Physical fitness is a possibility for sports that are out of season focusing on skill development.

00:01:14.659 --> 00:01:19.298
Students work on physical fitness at local gyms or with equipment available at the school

00:01:19.969 --> 00:01:25.419
Every semester the club offerings vary from hiking outdoors to calligraphy indoors

00:01:29.440 --> 00:01:33.060
Sports teams run for both boys and girls including

00:01:33.060 --> 00:01:35.680
basketbal,l volleybal,l badminton, and swimming

00:01:43.260 --> 00:01:47.800
Club experiences can be beneficial to supplemental applications to universities

00:01:48.140 --> 00:01:53.700
and we encourage students to make the most of everything the club system has to offer.

